{"tid":1078868,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《假面酒店》破《HERO》紀錄成木村拓哉在香港最賣座日本片(450萬港幣)","createTime":"2019-03-26T14:06:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T14:10:43.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"807f586d3ffca168c6e957c38c58d61795896c84","tid":1078868,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"木村拓哉及長澤正美主演，東野圭吾推理小說改編電影《假面酒店》自上周在港開畫以來走勢凌厲，上映首日即奪開畫電影票房冠軍。《假面酒店》在周末更持續強勢成為開畫電影周末冠軍，短短4日累積票房已衝破400萬大關。<br />\n<br />\n上映首日即奪開畫冠軍，而且截至3月25日，《假面酒店》上映不足5日票房已錄得逾451萬，極速打破同樣由木村拓哉主演、鈴木雅之執導的大熱電影《HERO》總票房紀錄（逾441萬），成為木村拓哉從影以來在港最賣座的日本電影。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2306613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2306613&d=l9j%2BX5M8xayYNSKzl1ZQhsmKZra6PqY6jPBlhHcv87Y%3D&h=c1a6ac26\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2306613</a>"},{"pid":"24a6aadf4ff9ed919bbe9b9e65525a631a62f5c3","tid":1078868,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"聽左<br />\n<br />\n真心麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7557031e21e5cdbba5cf1daf203d153e5ccbb610","tid":1078868,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n<br />\n真心麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb83f9319f782bed7f24fda3e27f78aaccb58d9","tid":1078868,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7557031e21e5cdbba5cf1daf203d153e5ccbb610","tid":1078868,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"睇左<br />\n<br />\n真心麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"真心都係咁話<br />\n如果真係要破紀錄<br />\n寧願佢之前做反派果套檢察狂人破<br />\n果套質素好好多<br />\n可惜香港文化沙漠 啲人只會揀啲望落易睇既戲去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}